<Body><Title>安理会谴责也门恐怖袭击事件</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2014年3月26日</ReportTime>
	<Content><Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s1">新华网联合国</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">３月２５日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">电</Denoter></Event>（记者倪红梅　顾震球）<Event eid="e2" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s2">联合国安理会</Participant><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">２５日</Time>发表<Means mid="m2" type="method">媒体</Means><Denoter did="d2" type="statement">声明</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e3" type="thoughtevent">强烈<Denoter did="d3" type="statement">谴责</Denoter></Event>２<Event eid="e4"><Time tid="t4" type="relTime">４日</Time>发生在<Location lid="l4">也门东部</Location>、造成多名士兵死亡的<Denoter did="d4" type="emergency">恐怖袭击</Denoter></Event>，并<Event eid="e5" type="thoughtevent"><Denoter did="d5" type="statement">重申</Denoter></Event>要坚决<Event eid="e6"><Denoter did="d6" type="action">打击</Denoter>一切形式的<Object oid="o6">恐怖主义</Object></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e7" type="thoughtevent"><Object sid="s7">声明</Object><Denoter did="d7" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e8" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s8">安理会</Participant><Denoter did="d8" type="statement">重申</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e9">任何形式的<Object sid="s9">恐怖主义</Object>都是对<Object oid="o9">国际和平与安全</Object>构成的最严重<Denoter did="d9" type="perception">威胁</Denoter>之一</Event>，<Event eid="e10"><Object  oid="o10,o11">恐怖主义</Object>不论发生在何时何地、由<Participant sid="s10">谁</Participant><Denoter did="d10" type="operation">实施</Denoter>、出于何种动机，都是犯罪行为</Event>且<Event eid="e11" polarity="negative">无法<Denoter did="d11" type="operation">开脱</Denoter><Object oid="o11">罪责</Object></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e12" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s12">安理会</Participant><Time tid="t12" type="relTime">同时</Time><Denoter did="d12" type="statement">强调</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e13">必须将这些恐怖主义行径的<Participant oid="o13">实施者、组织者、资助者和支持者</Participant><Denoter did="d13" type="operation">绳之以法</Denoter></Event>，同时<Event eid="e14"><Denoter did="d14" type="operation">敦促</Denoter><Participant oid="o14">所有国家</Participant></Event><Event eid="e15">按照<Means mid="m15" type="method">国际法和安理会相关决议规定的义务</Means>，在这些方面与<Participant sid="s15">也门当局</Participant>积极<Denoter did="d15" type="action">合作</Denoter>。</Event></Sentence></Paragraph>
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e16" type="thoughtevent">也门东部哈德拉毛省<Participant sid="s16">安全官员</Participant><Time tid="t16" type="relTime">２４日</Time><Denoter did="d16" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e17">位于该省的一处<Object oid="o17">政府军军营</Object><Time tid="t17" type="relTime">当天</Time>遭到“<Participant sid="s17">基地”组织武装人员</Participant><Denoter did="d17" type="action">袭击</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e18">造成<Participant sid="s18">２４名政府军士兵</Participant><Denoter did="d18" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e19"><Participant sid="s19">１人</Participant><Denoter did="d19" type="stateChange">重伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e20" polarity="negative" type="thoughtevent">“<Participant sid="s20">基地”组织分支</Participant><Time tid="t20" type="relTime">当时</Time>未<Denoter did="d20" type="statement">宣布</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e21">对这起袭击<Object oid="o21">事件</Object><Denoter did="d21" type="perception">负责</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph></Content>

